## Commands Quick Reference

- Install deps: `bun install` (Bun ≥1.1)
- Dev server: `bun run dev` → `http://localhost:3000`
- Build: `bun run build` (bundles + type-checks)
- Lint: `bun run lint` (fail on warnings). Autofix: `bun run lint --fix`
- Format: `bun run format`
- Tests: `bun run test` (Vitest). Coverage: `bunx vitest --coverage`
- DB: `bun run db:migrate` (after `supabase start`)

Security & config:
- Copy `.env.example` to `.env.local`. Keep Supabase keys and Caixa tokens out of VCS.
- Rotate Supabase service keys quarterly; note updates in [docs/SYSTEM_PROMPT.md](mdc:docs/SYSTEM_PROMPT.md).

